platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: A hugely ambitious action blockbuster, Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas is filled with sharp satire, fascinatingly flawed characters, and a huge variety of ways to play. Explore the cities and countryside of a vividly realized fictional version of the southwestern United States. You can tackle story-driven quests, gorge on fast food, outrun the police, or obey every traffic lightits up to you. This enormous game deftly displays Rockstars unique mastery of open-world design, and it never fails to entertain.
